data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Skipcha Subdivision of Harker Heights, TX! This well-maintained two-story residence offers a spacious, flat backyard ideal for outdoor gatherings and play. Inside, the open kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Enjoy the warmth of the wood-burning fireplace in one of the multiple living areas, creating a cozy ambiance for relaxation or entertaining guests. Mature trees adorn the front yard, offering shade and natural beauty. Conveniently situated, this home a drive away from from various amenities such as restaurants, parks, schools, shopping centers, and gyms, providing easy access to everyday conveniences. With its inviting layout and prime location, this home is ready to welcome its next homeowners to create lasting memories. Schedule your showing before it’s gone!
